quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,Naho twari kubasabira impuhwe nukubakurira ingorane zabo bafise ntankeka bari kubandanya muri iyo nzira y’ubuzimire bwabo naho borengana bari muri ayo mabi yabo barimwo
  23,76,Mu vy’ukuri twarabahanye mugabo ntibigeze batumbera ku Muremyi wabo canke ngo bayigamburukire
  23,77,"Kugeza aho twabugurira umuryango w’ibihano bikaze cane, aho niho baciye bihebura"
  23,78,"Nayo\tniyo\tyabaremeye\tamatwi\tn’amaso\thamwe\tn’imitima,\tmugabo nibakeyi cane bashima"
  23,79,Nayo niyo yabakwirije kuri iy’Isi kandi n’iwe niho muzokoranywa
  23,80,"Nayo niyo irema igatako ikica, n’ihindagurika ry’ibintu vyose haba ihindagurika ry’Ijoro canke ihindagurika ry’Umutaga vyose nirwiwe, mbega mwebwe ntimutegera"
  23,81,Ahubwo bavuga yuko ivyavuzwe n’abantu baho hambere
  23,82,"Bavuze bati:- mbega nitwasandaba n’ukuba ivu n’amagufa masa, niho tuzozurwa"
  23,83,"Twaremerewe aho hambere ibi vyose twebwe hamwe n’abavyeyi bacu, mugabo ibi vyose ntivyabayeho mugabo n’inkuru z’ububeshi zabaho hambere"
  23,84,"Nuvuge uti:- iy’Isi turiko n’ibirimwo vyose nivyande? Nimwaba muzi n’ikintu nakimwe"
  23,85,"Nabo bazokwishura bati:- ni vy’Imana, na wewe nuvuge uti:- mbega mwebwe ntimwibuka"
  23,86,"Vuga uti:- ni nde muremyi w’Amajuru yose uko ari indwi n’Umuremyi w’inyegamo yiwe y’iteka"
  23,87,"Bazokwishura bati:- ni vy’Imana nawe nubishure uti :- mbega ntimuyitinya"
  23,88,"Vuga uti:- ni nde mukuboko kwiwe harimwo ubwami bw’ibintu vyose, nawe akaba ariwe acungereye ibintu vyose, kandi ntagicungerewe gusumbawe nimwaba mufise ubumenyi buhagije"
  23,89,"Nabo bazokwishura bati :- ubwo bubasha nubw’Imana nawe nuvuge uti :- none ni kuki muhendwa gutyo"